138
00:10:21,830 --> 00:10:22,870
Buggeuggom?

139
00:10:28,170 --> 00:10:30,710
Kelihatannya, dia mengetahui sesuatu.

140
00:10:35,180 --> 00:10:36,750
Saya sudah bicara pada Sa Do Chan,

141
00:10:37,220 --> 00:10:39,680
